name: PEEK KING
description: PEEK KING is the first cubicle experiment on a modular level for a syntax crystal. By positioning the crystals in such a lattice structure and added 3 strings, we have successfully created the illusion of three blocks sitting on a floor. This also creates a completely separate image of crystals floating above a layered lattice of crystals laying horizontal connected by strings. As we journey into more and more complex structures that lie within, we discover a whole new universe of possibilities, as absurd as they may be. I particularly love these and will be experimenting more in the near future.
